content: cygaar: Merged two PRs this month, with the most significant being #2207 which added AGW support to the Abstract plugin (+4839/-1868 lines). Made 8 commits across 11 files (+621/-400 lines), with work primarily focused on configuration files (50%) followed by code and documentation (25% each). Activity was sporadic, occurring on only 3 days this month, with contributions split between other work (63%), bug fixes (25%), and feature development (13%).
